### Obtener registro de auditoría por ID
GET http://localhost:{{port}}/api/audit/1 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar auditoría (sin filtros)
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/audit/list HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "page": 0,
    "rows": 20,
    "search": "",
    "order_by": "a.created_at",
    "order": "DESC"
}

###

### Listar auditoría filtrada por tabla
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/audit/list HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "page": 0,
    "rows": 20,
    "search": "",
    "order_by": "a.created_at",
    "order": "DESC",
    "params": {
        "tableName": "usuario"
    }
}

###

### Listar auditoría filtrada por acción
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/audit/list HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "page": 0,
    "rows": 20,
    "search": "",
    "order_by": "a.created_at",
    "order": "DESC",
    "params": {
        "action": "UPDATE"
    }
}

###

### Listar auditoría filtrada por usuario y rango de fechas
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/audit/list HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "page": 0,
    "rows": 20,
    "search": "",
    "order_by": "a.created_at",
    "order": "DESC",
    "params": {
        "userId": 1,
        "dateFrom": "2024-01-01T00:00:00",
        "dateTo": "2024-12-31T23:59:59"
    }
}

###

### Listar auditoría filtrada por IP de origen
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/audit/list HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "page": 0,
    "rows": 20,
    "search": "",
    "order_by": "a.created_at",
    "order": "DESC",
    "params": {
        "ipOrigin": "127.0.0.1"
    }
}

###
